description: Commands to manage Config Server git repository in Azure Spring Cloud.

commands.name: az spring-cloud config-server git repo add
commands.summary: Add a new repository of git property of Config Server.
commands.syntax:
az spring-cloud config-server git repo add --name
                                           --repo-name
                                           --resource-group
                                           --uri
                                           [--defer]
                                           [--host-key]
                                           [--host-key-algorithm]
                                           [--label]
                                           [--password]
                                           [--pattern]
                                           [--private-key]
                                           [--search-paths]
                                           [--strict-host-key-checking]
                                           [--username]

commands.name: az spring-cloud config-server git repo list
commands.summary: List all repositories of git property of Config Server.
commands.syntax:
az spring-cloud config-server git repo list --name
                                            --resource-group
                                            [--defer]

commands.name: az spring-cloud config-server git repo remove
commands.summary: Remove an existing repository of git property of Config Server.
commands.syntax:
az spring-cloud config-server git repo remove --name
                                              --repo-name
                                              --resource-group
                                              [--defer]

commands.name: az spring-cloud config-server git repo update
commands.summary: Override an existing repository of git property of Config Server, will totally override the old one.
commands.syntax:
az spring-cloud config-server git repo update --name
                                              --repo-name
                                              --resource-group
                                              [--defer]
                                              [--host-key]
                                              [--host-key-algorithm]
                                              [--label]
                                              [--password]
                                              [--pattern]
                                              [--private-key]
                                              [--search-paths]
                                              [--strict-host-key-checking]
                                              [--uri]
                                              [--username]
